  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p>Rinse the <strong>freekeh</strong> in a sieve under the tap, then add it to a pot with 500ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span>&nbsp;cold water and bring to a boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20 min or until tender, but with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-1-new-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-1-new-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-1-new-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-1-new-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-1-new-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> chicken</strong> and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong>, then<strong>&nbsp;</strong>cook on each side for 3-4 min</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Boil a little kettle water (for step 4)&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-2-new-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-2-new-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-2-new-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-2-new-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-2-new-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>onion</strong> to the chicken&nbsp;and cook for a further 2-3 min, stirring until glossy</p>\r\n<p>Line a baking tray with <strong>tin foil</strong> and transfer the onions and chicken to the tray</p>\r\n<p>Drizzle the onions with the <strong>pomegranate molasses</strong>, season with <strong>pepper</strong> and put the tray in the oven for 10-15 min, or until the chicken is cooked through</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-3-new-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-3-new-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-3-new-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-3-new-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-3-new-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>tahini</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>honey</strong></p>\r\n<p>Gradually add 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong>, a tablespoon at a time, and whisk (or stir with a fork) vigorously until a thin glossy sauce forms</p>\r\n<p>Season generously with <strong>salt</strong> - this is your tahini sauce</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-4-new-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-4-new-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-4-new-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-4-new-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-4-new-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>walnuts</strong> to a separate baking tray or oven-proof dish</p>\r\n<p>Put them in the oven for 4 min, or until the walnuts have slightly darkened in colour</p>\r\n<p>Once toasted, leave the nuts to cool</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong>&nbsp;finely,<strong>&nbsp;</strong>including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>Chop the cooled, toasted <strong>walnuts</strong> coarsely</p>\r\n<p>Drain the cooked <strong>freekeh</strong>, return it to the cooking pot and season it with a pinch of&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-6-new-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-6-new-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-6-new-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-6-new-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-6-new-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add half of the <strong>parsley</strong> (save the rest for garnish),&nbsp;<strong>walnuts</strong>, <strong>onions</strong> and any cooking juices from the tray into the freekeh and stir to combine</p>\r\n<p>Slice the <strong>chicken </strong>finely with a sharp knife&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-7-new-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-7-new-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-7-new-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/428.step-7-new-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
